## Comandos útiles
```bash
# Iniciar sistema
cd infrastructure && docker compose up --build

# Ver logs
docker compose logs -f

# Limpiar todo
docker compose down -v && docker system prune -a -f

# Entrar al contenedor
docker compose exec hardware bash

# Ver logs del hardware
docker compose logs hardware-1
